```json
{
  "application": "NWChem",
  "software": [
    "Intel Fortran/C/C++ compilers 2013",
    "Intel MKL 2013 math library",
    "PGI compiler",
    "libnuma",
    "OpenMPI-Intel 4.0.1",
    "Python"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "ppn": 12,
    "walltime": "200:00:00",
    "memory": "40g",
    "queue": "batch",
    "scratch_directory": "/mnt/local/$USER/$PBS_JOBID"
  },
  "environment_variables": [
    "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
    "PATH",
    "TMPDIR",
    "NWCHEM_EXECUTABLE",
    "OMP_NUM_THREADS",
    "MKL_NUM_THREADS",
    "MKL_DYNAMIC",
    "OMP_DYNAMIC",
    "PMIX_MCA_gds"
  ],
  "input_files": [
    "$PBS_O_WORKDIR/TMS.start_geom.xyz",
    "$PBS_O_WORKDIR/$project.nw"
  ],
  "output_files": [
    "$PBS_O_WORKDIR/$project.out",
    "$PBS_O_WORKDIR/TMS_geom*"
  ]
}
```
